  "page": "Leo Tyrell (son of Gareth)",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Tyrell\" title=\"House Tyrell\"><img alt=\"House Tyrell.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/31/House_Tyrell.svg/50px-House_Tyrell.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/31/House_Tyrell.svg/75px-House_Tyrell.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/31/House_Tyrell.svg/100px-House_Tyrell.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> High Steward</span><br />Leo Tyrell</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Tyrell\" title=\"House Tyrell\"><img alt=\"House Tyrell.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/31/House_Tyrell.svg/50px-House_Tyrell.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/31/House_Tyrell.svg/75px-House_Tyrell.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/31/House_Tyrell.svg/100px-House_Tyrell.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/High_Steward\" title=\"High Steward\">High Steward</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Tyrell\" title=\"House Tyrell\">House Tyrell</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Andal\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Andal\">Andal</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Father</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Gareth_Tyrell\" title=\"Gareth Tyrell\">Gareth Tyrell</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Leo Tyrell</b> was a head of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Tyrell\" title=\"House Tyrell\">House Tyrell</a> and the second Tyrell <a href=\"/index.php/High_Steward\" title=\"High Steward\">High Steward</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a>. He was the son of <a href=\"/index.php/Gareth_Tyrell\" title=\"Gareth Tyrell\">Gareth Tyrell</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Leo_Tyrell_(son_of_Gareth)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Gareth and Leo performed their duties to <a href=\"/index.php/House_Gardener\" title=\"House Gardener\">House Gardener</a> so well, the Gardeners made the office of High Steward hereditary.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafhouse_tyrell.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafhouse_tyrell.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Leo_Tyrell_(son_of_Gareth)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\"><a